subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Monica Puig, Tsvetana Pironkova and Karin Knapp, who all reached the Round of 16 at Wimbledon last year while ranked outside the top 50, lost in the first round Tuesday.
